title: Cozy 1bd Apartment Available with Fresh Updates by Hamline University!
posting_body: ['This cozy unit features a bay window and original hardwood floors in the kitchen, private side entrance, and spacious bedroom space.', 'New cabinetry in kitchen being installed upon posting this ad!', 'The building features on-site laundry, ample surface parking in the back, controlled access to the building, and 24/7 emergency maintenance.', 'Great location, directly across from Hancock Recreational Center/Hamline University and 1 block from public transit bus stops,  thriving Snelling Ave business district, and Hamline University.', 'Utilities include: heat, water, trash, recycling, and sewage', 'Tenants are only responsible for electricity and cable/internet as desired.', 'Cat friendly.', 'One time pet deposit of $200 and no cat rent.', 'ESA animals welcome.', 'Application fee is $25 per adult tenant.', "Deposit is set based on application; range from $600-equivalent of first month's rent.", 'Rental requirements:', '2.5x monthly income as a combined household', '625+ credit score', 'Positive rental history.', 'No prior evictions/unlawful detainers.', 'No felonies', 'Sorry, we do not work with Section 8/GRH.', 'If this sounds like your ideal place, please reach out to Savannah by email or', 'show contact info', '(text/call)']
